cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CL 

The paper proposes a new family of optimization criteria for variational auto-encoding models and provides conditions for learning informative latent features and recovering the data distribution. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), or computational linguistics (cs.CL) sub-categories.
